lead_paragraph: Most Americans have a favorable view of former U.S. Secretary of State Hillary Clinton and think she will win the 2016 presidential election, according to a Reuters/Ipsos poll released on Thursday.

headline.main: More Than Half of Americans Approve of Hillary Clinton: Reuters/Ipsos Poll
